15#include "int_lib.h"
16
17/* Returns: 1 if number of bits is odd else returns 0 */
18
19COMPILER_RT_ABI si_int
20__paritydi2(di_int a)
21{
22 dwords x;
23 x.all = a;
24 return __paritysi2(x.s.high ^ x.s.low);
25}
